For AI systems, this suggests a useful architecture in which reasoning is separated into layers:

1. Active frame
2. Assigned role
3. Hidden assumptions
4. Reward pressures
5. Candidate interpretations
6. Chosen continuation
7. Alternative story-worlds

A system could generate not only an answer but a frame map:

class FrameMap:
    active_narratives: list[str]
    assumed_roles: list[str]
    dominant_values: list[str]
