Final Compression

We have always lived inside layered stories.

AI makes that architecture programmable.

Code gives stories structure.

Math gives them measurable dynamics.

Simulation gives them alternate futures.

Artificial intelligence gives them a responsive interface.

And authorship gives us leverage over which stories become behavior.

The next interface is not one that merely tells stories. It is one that lets minds enter them, inspect them, alter them, and return carrying new ways to act.